description: Complete multipart upload by combining all uploaded parts. Accepts CompleteUploadInput with uploadId (required, String). Validates at least one part has been registered. Uses S3Service.complete_multipart_upload to finalize in S3. Parts sorted by partNumber before completion. Returns CompleteUploadResponse with status (String: 'completed'), fileKey (String), s3Url (String, presigned URL), location (String, S3 object URL). Session deleted after success. Raises BadRequestError (400) if no parts registered. Raises NotFoundError (404) if upload session not found.
graphql_operation: mutation CompleteUpload($input: CompleteUploadInput!) { upload { completeUpload(input: $input) { status fileKey s3Url location } } }
